# Search Boeing Skills

Run the Boeing CLI skill search command with the user's query:

```sh
boeing skills search --non-interactive "<query>"
```

If the user did not provide a query, list all available skills by running:

```sh
boeing skills search --non-interactive
```

Show the matching skills returned by the CLI.
